00:40:15.410 --> 00:40:18.840
Perhaps foreknew heaven's design

00:40:18.840 --> 00:40:21.900
Thus fled destiny's trace

00:40:22.260 --> 00:40:25.130
Migrating toward you

00:40:26.570 --> 00:40:29.070
But worldly customs permit only

00:40:29.070 --> 00:40:32.560
Our fleeting meetings

00:40:32.580 --> 00:40:36.320
Granting us floods
strong enough to wound

00:40:36.320 --> 00:40:40.120
Each other deeply

00:40:40.730 --> 00:40:43.080
Fear one stroke wrong in time's flow

00:40:43.080 --> 00:40:47.260
Passion fills the page,
leaving only foolish longing

00:40:47.560 --> 00:40:49.950
Fear sincerity trespassing half a step

